            . I am a constable. I saw Frearson in the waggon.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210214-75-person848">
                  EDWARD 
                  HAWKES
               <interp inst="t18210214-75-person848" type="surname" value="HAWKES"></interp>
