               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210214-75-person849">
                  JOHN 
                  DAY
               <interp inst="t18210214-75-person849" type="surname" value="DAY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210214-75-person849" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210214-75-person849" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . My mother lives at Hammersmith. The barley-meal was delivered, and we returned all the empty sacks we had. They were all marked with Mr. Stanbrough's name.</p>
               <p>ROBINSON - <rs id="t18210214-75-verdict483" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210214-75-verdict483" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 28.</p>
